<plot>'My Pen Pal: An African Adventure" is a children's documentary about an 10 year-old California girl who travels to Tanzania to meet her pen pal. Along the way she gets up close to African wildlife at Ngorongoro Crater and The Serengeti. She also has an authentic Massai Village experience.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?384695</url></doc>
